@startuml
title analysis.build_manifest - Responsibilities
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "build_manifest.py\npython -m analysis.build_manifest" as manifest
database "results/\nraw JSONL" as results
file "manifest-<run_id>.json" as mf

manifest --> results : list JSONL files\n+ parse metadata
manifest --> mf : write expected coverage\n+ primary component type\n+ language profile

note right of manifest
Makefile target: manifest
Inputs:
- --results-dir results/
- --run-id <uuid>
- --expected <metric:tool:variant,...>

Output:
- results/manifest-<run_id>.json
end note
@enduml
